'''Doron''' or '''Dorio''', as it is said to be written in some manuscripts, is a city mentioned only by [[Pliny the Elder|Pliny]] and located in [[Cilicia Trachea|Cilicia Tracheia]],<ref>Plin. ''H.N.'', v. 27</ref> Some scholars have equated the city to [[Darieium]] or [[Dorieium]] in [[Phrygia]] mentioned by [[Stephanus of Byzantium]].<ref>Steph. B. ''s.v.'' {{lang|grc|Δαρίειον}}; Steph. B. ''s.v.'' {{lang|grc|Δορίειον}}.</ref> 

